{"tid":700324,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死一件]「NEWS」手越祐也爆灌酒未成年少女","createTime":"2018-06-13T09:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T01:18:06.000Z","uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"17313b9d5336f89eb88d0ef5034598b40aee7c06","tid":700324,"uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:17:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傑尼斯再沾腥！「NEWS」手越祐也爆灌酒未成年少女<br />\n建立時間：2018/06/13 16:35<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/13/171706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F171706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2ca7430f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本傑尼斯團「NEWS」成員小山慶一郎和加藤成亮被爆灌酒未成年少女，小山還因此丟掉主持棒，並被「冷凍」。沒想到，今天《週刊文春》又驚爆該團另一位成員手越祐也和未成年少女飲酒作樂，雜誌還握有影像檔案，明天就會曝光。<br />\n<br />\n週刊報導，他去年12月和一群男女開派對，同席的女生有兩名分別只有19和17 歲，但17歲少女否認當天有喝酒。傑尼斯則表示，會加強管理偶像們的私生活。他們的前師兄山口達也才因為猥褻未成年少女葬送演藝事業，「NEWS」成員小山慶一郎和加藤成亮日前被爆灌酒未成年少女，現在又是手越祐也和未成年一起開派對，都證明了傑尼斯的管理螺絲似乎已經鬆了。（陳穎／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20180613/1372633\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180613%2F1372633&d=FV2XEAZaZhoVNZDUrCLvDZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=68dd6580\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20180613%2F1372633&h=108a8095\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20180613/1372633</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"496e4109a8dc5cfeb5ee78fe705b44c336c6e569","tid":700324,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T09:21:19.000Z","msg":"手越到底有咩吸引 三上又食過柏木又食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a93065a74fc203446a9eaef32f149e5a1c852f","